{"tid":30040,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今日返工，90後新同事竟然唔幫HR換水","createTime":"2016-12-09T03:18:50.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T05:56:45.000Z","uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dac36d411dca4b6f0ae15c07eeead8657375bbb5","tid":30040,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T03:18:50.000Z","msg":"今日一返工就去裝水飲 岩岩好裝到滿 部水機就無水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n渣渣林返埋位扮做野廢事比人叫去換水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好死唔死個肥婆HR走去裝水 佢一發覺無水就行出黎點個90後新同事幫佢換水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知新同事話一桶水幾公斤都拎唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲話咩你肚腩舊肉都重過桶水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後個肥婆HR就嬲爆爆咁衝過黎叫我去換水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉屌 真係多得佢唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45436b82c930b84de18ecdb4bc273ecdcf45c670","tid":30040,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T03:34:20.000Z","msg":"唉 搬到手都軟埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ba0a1530c3688be3eed9a593047b3e9b7907f4","tid":30040,"uid":57665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T03:38:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唉 搬到手都軟埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n慘過番印度"},{"pid":"6b63caf6be0f17ca5808715bd79d30ac1c17b10a","tid":30040,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7037dd9b9099ada41ee316ca48d95d3f478600c3","tid":30040,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:53:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />